                " Universitaet, Muenchen."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERMUN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Munich Research Reactor."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The samples were irradiated in the",
                " graphite reflector of the reactor."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The thermal neutron flux was 1.6E+13 neutrons/cm-sq*Se",
                " and 1.4E+13 neutrons/cm-sq*sec for the two samples,",
                " respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Two samples of about 555 Mg uranium enriched to about",
                " 90% U-235. Each sample consisted of 9 chips",
                " of 55-65 Mg of uranium metal. Each chip was wrapped in",
                " aluminum foil (20 um thick). The chips were place in",
                " larger aluminum cans, three by three, and three such",
                " cans formed one sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation time was about 30 days."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Chemical separation"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A coaxial Ge(Li) detector with a 16.9%",
                " photopeak efficiancy relative to a 3 inch * 3 inch",
                " NaI(Tl) crystal and a resolution of 2.1 keV for the",
                " 1.33 MeV gamma-ray of Co-60 was used for detection of",
                " the 478. keV gamma-ray of Be-7 and radiation from",
                " Ba-140 used a monitor for the number of fissions.",
                " The Be-samples were also counted in a calibrated",
                " low-background gas flow window counter provided with",
                " an anticoincidence guard counter to measure possible",
                " beta activity of 1.6e+06 yr Be-10. the same beta-",
                " counter was used to measure the beta activity of Si-32",
                " and its daughter p-32 with half-life 14.28 d."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The number of fissions in the irradiated U-235 sample",
                " was determined from the amount of Ba-140 produced in",
                " the sample. This number was determined to be",
                " 1.5e+19 and 0.9e+19 for the two samples, respectively",
                " Since no or very small evidences for excistance",
                " of activity were observed, only upper limits for",
                " fission yields are given."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " For",
                " - detector efficiency",
                " - chemical yield",
                " - burn-up of produced fission products"
              ]
            }
          ],
